Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.31,0:01:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奠定了集權制官僚國家基礎的聖德太子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對他是否真的存在表示質疑的人也不少
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 你們知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:47.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有個聖德太子騎著馬飛上天空去了富士山的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.74,0:01:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}少騙人了 新井老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.37,0:01:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}馬怎麼可能會飛上天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.34,0:02:13.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從富士山回來之後 我有些不敢看日向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.06,0:02:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向好像也很少見的顧慮我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.06,0:02:19.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我們這樣的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.25,0:02:30.50,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(570,426)}致我親愛的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得收拾下背包裏面呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:04.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭燈結果都沒用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.82,0:03:08.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我什麼時候買的玩偶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有那個羊羹 那是日向的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.79,0:03:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣啊 葵她沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那之後就沒了精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.09,0:03:28.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,短信我也不知道該怎麼發
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是楓在就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:37.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去北阿爾卑斯縱走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去穿越大巖棱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:47.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要去見見葵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概 現在還是不要去管她的好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:04:00.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 她一定會打起精神來的 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:03.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.13,0:04:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我會打給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.16,0:04:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是暑假 我卻無所事事 這樣好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.92,0:04:52.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那天起 心裏就好像裂開了一個大口子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.13,0:04:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管做什麼都不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:08.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:11.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.87,0:05:21.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵的信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:26.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向和心夏寫的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從富士山郵寄到這裏 是現在到呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.22,0:05:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很熱的 戴上帽子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天覽山 高尾山 三增卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後還來了富士山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.13,0:06:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天再一起去回憶中的大山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.34,0:06:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼日向寫的這麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最開始是這裏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.11,0:06:36.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 葵 爬哪個山呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最開始爬那邊的小山丘…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:42.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能這樣隨便呢 不受歡迎的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.45,0:06:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟受不受歡迎沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.75,0:06:47.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近處的小山丘的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.29,0:06:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會遇難的哦 我還不想死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:57.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明那麼害怕 又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.09,0:07:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前明明還上氣不接下氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比以前還能爬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.10,0:07:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.43,0:07:05.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:10.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像散步一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好開心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.53,0:07:19.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前是走這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:21.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這邊走走看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.29,0:07:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能有點陡峭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.96,0:07:36.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:39.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經登頂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.66,0:08:05.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.29,0:08:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才明信片寄到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.34,0:08:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為寫著天覽山 就有點懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向是來幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:28.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散步 真是巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.06,0:08:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打算等下去多峰主山
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.81,0:08:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多峰主山?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這前面也有大山哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:40.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過說 從這裏開始才是真正的登山吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵也一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.29,0:08:51.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦 好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.63,0:08:57.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:59.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:11.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(662,446)}注意蝮蛇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏叫做回首坡道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.03,0:09:26.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說很久很久以前有位大人在這裏回了好幾次頭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.49,0:09:28.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都沒說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.84,0:09:41.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.79,0:10:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是天空樹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:21.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高尾山也看得到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.47,0:10:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:33.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去了那裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.31,0:10:43.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那以後 我心裏一直像裂開了一個大口子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:46.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失敗了很痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:48.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同樣也非常不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.74,0:10:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我還是想再登山
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那我們一起登吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:02.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢的 一點一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:04.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天 也能登上回憶中的大山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:05.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:09.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對的 摔倒了再爬起來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.68,0:11:14.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算一個人很痛苦 有肯陪伴我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.60,0:11:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃羊羹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:23.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向之前給我的那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你一半
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.86,0:11:30.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為羊羹啊 你是老爺爺麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總覺得好火大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.16,0:11:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來就是你買的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:45.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 一步一步 慢慢來就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:48.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是一點一點 只要向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.42,0:11:52.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為總有一天 雙腳會到達山頂的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天見 yahoo
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:59.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未完待續
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:07.64,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}並んで歩いてたら 自然に
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:11.60,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}二人三脚なってたね
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:18.36,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}透明リボンで結ぼう
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:23.28,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}一人で描く夢は……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:27.49,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}ふたりなら立体的になる
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:31.29,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}キュンときて上昇! 行こう!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:34.16,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}スタッカートみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:38.09,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}胸を叩くワクワク感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:38.92,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}それに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:44.47,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}付き合ってくれる　俺の合う
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:46.80,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}Dear My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:50.14,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}地球色パレット
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:54.10,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}混ぜて明日は何色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:55.02,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}不思議
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:10:00.19,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}不安より楽しみの容量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:04.53,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}が増えたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.11,crj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}明天ヤッホー
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:07.64,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}兩人並肩行走 自然地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:11.60,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}變成了兩人三腳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:18.36,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}透明的緞帶將我們緊緊連結在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.27,0:09:23.28,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}就算是一人所描繪的夢想……
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.53,0:09:27.49,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}兩個人的話就會變得可以實現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.53,0:09:31.25,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}心跳正在加速！一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:34.16,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}像那跳躍的音符一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:38.09,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}敲擊心靈的興奮感
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:38.92,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}還有那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:44.47,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}在我身旁陪著我的你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.72,0:09:46.80,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}Dear My Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:50.14,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}地球色的調色板上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.26,0:09:54.10,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}明天又是屬於何種顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:55.02,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}不可思議的是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:10:00.19,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}比起不安 開心的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.65,0:10:04.53,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}卻漸漸高漲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.70,0:10:07.11,crC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}明天見 呀吼

